      <title>波兰立法者指责央行行长债券购买失误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/polish-lawmakers-accuse-central-bank-chief-of-bond-buying-faults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克所在政党的议员将对该国央行行长提出一系列冗长的指控，作为最终寻求罢免行长亚当·格拉平斯基的动议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/polish-lawmakers-accuse-central-bank-chief-of-bond-buying-faults</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
