    <item>
      <title>TikTok 受到美国参议院主要民主党人的新审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/tiktok-draws-fresh-scrutiny-from-key-us-senate-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院商务主席玛丽亚·坎特韦尔 (Maria Cantwell) 表示，在周三与美国情报官员举行机密简报后，她正在考虑就 TikTok 和社交媒体举行公开听证会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/tiktok-draws-fresh-scrutiny-from-key-us-senate-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥官员称萨利纳斯集团欠债 38 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/salinas-companies-owe-3-8-billion-mexican-tax-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国税务机关负责人周三表示，里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 控制的四家公司欠政府 630 亿比索（合 38 亿美元），总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔 (Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador) 与这位亿万富翁之间的争端日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/salinas-companies-owe-3-8-billion-mexican-tax-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:52:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登关于汽车排放的最新规定将促进电动汽车销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周三采取行动，遏制美国汽车和轻型卡车的污染，实行严格的尾气排放限制，这将迫使汽车制造商迅速提高电池电动和插电式混合动力车型的销量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官允许对其对检察官威利斯罗曼史的裁决提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和几名共同被告获准对佐治亚州法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决称富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯尽管与一名高级检察官有恋情，但仍可以继续参与州选举干预案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰总理预计美国最早将于本月提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总理表示，美国受阻的资金最早可能在本月到达，而且为前线招募新兵的规模可能少于军方最初支持的 50 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
